{"data":[{"date":"15:47 30/07","title":"V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Messi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/vo-chong-messi-lien-tuc-gap-nguoi-noi-tieng-trong-ky-nghi-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt VIP ch\u1ecdn Ibiza \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u00e1t, g\u1eb7p si\u00eau sao Argentina v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh chung.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf qu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3o Turks v\u00e0 Caicos \u1edf v\u00f9ng Carib\u00ea, Messi v\u00e0 Antonella Roccuzzo \u0111ang \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf Ibiza v\u1edbi ba \u0111\u1ee9a con t\u1ea1i Ibiza, T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 \u0111ang tranh th\u1ee7 x\u1ea3 h\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Messi t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Barca, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Messi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Messi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/cc-3730-1532830771.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi v\u00e0 v\u1ee3 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng ca s\u0129 Gloria Estefan (th\u1ee9 hai t\u1eeb ph\u1ea3i sang). \u1ea2nh: NN.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh tr\u00ean du thuy\u1ec1n ra kh\u01a1i t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u01b0\u1edbc bi\u1ec3n xanh, v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Messi c\u0169ng th\u1ec9nh tho\u1ea3ng l\u00ean b\u1edd, \u0111i th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c b\u1eefa t\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3o. Ch\u1ed7 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng sang tr\u1ecdng \"Lio\" l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Messi v\u00e0 Antonella Roccuzzo g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng si\u00eau sao Argentina m\u1edbi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh chung c\u00f9ng tay v\u1ee3t Nadal. Ng\u00e0y 27/7, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 ca s\u0129 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 g\u1ed1c Cuba Gloria Estefan. Trong su\u1ed1t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Ibiza, gia \u0111\u00ecnh Messi c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \"c\u1eb7p k\u00e8\" c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Fabregas. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea v\u00e0 v\u1ee3 m\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1edbi Daniella Semaan t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ti\u1ec7c sau \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Sant Miquel tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00eam ti\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Ibiza, Messi v\u00e0 Antonella Roccuzzo c\u0169ng t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t danh th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 Chelsea - l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Fabregas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi, DJ Sebastian Gamboa t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c show di\u1ec5n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3o T\u00e2y Ban Nha, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n thu h\u00fat nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng. Messi v\u00e0 v\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t m\u00ea nh\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129 qu\u00ea \u1edf \u0111\u1ea3o Ibiza n\u00e0y, \"ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u00fa v\u1ecb\".</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4839","checkdouble":"192329"},{"date":"15:51 30/07","title":"\u0110\u01b0a c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 sang M\u1ef9, Rooney v\u1eabn c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 \u1edf Anh","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/dua-ca-nha-sang-my-rooney-van-cai-tao-biet-thu-o-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o DC United quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng, b\u1ed5 sung ti\u1ec7n \u00edch cho n\u01a1i \u1edf t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u00f9ng Chesire, Anh c\u1ee7a Rooney v\u00e0 Coleen \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p. Theo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m m\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00eam. Trong \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1eadp trung l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng camera gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t kh\u1ee7ng ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n cao.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u01b0a gia \u0111\u00ecnh sang M\u1ef9, nh\u00e0 Rooney \u1edf Anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u01b0a gia \u0111\u00ecnh sang M\u1ef9, nh\u00e0 Rooney \u1edf Anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/cc-7752-1532829340.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 t\u1ea1i Anh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 Rooney \u0111ang n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p. \u1ea2nh: TS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fd do l\u00e0 Rooney - Coleen mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c v\u1edbi n\u1ea1n tr\u1ed9m c\u1eafp m\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n. N\u0103m 2016, khi Coleen c\u00f9ng l\u0169 tr\u1ebb t\u1edbi s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng xem m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Rooney, \"nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng m\u1eddi\" \u0111\u1ed9t nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 v\u00e0 l\u1ea5y \u0111i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1eadt gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb. V\u1ee5 \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1ee7 \u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m thu\u00ea c\u0169 trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 t\u00ean Robert McNamara. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb k\u1ebft \u00e1n hai n\u0103m 8 th\u00e1ng t\u00f9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb tr\u1ed9m h\u1ecfi th\u0103m bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 c\u00e0ng t\u0103ng cao khi Rooney \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ee3 con t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 sinh s\u1ed1ng khi anh t\u1edbi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o DC United m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, gia \u0111\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 d\u00e0nh kho\u1ea3ng n\u1eeda th\u1eddi gian trong n\u0103m \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf c\u1edd hoa v\u00e0 6 th\u00e1ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i v\u1edbi garage 6 xe, ph\u00f2ng chi\u1ebfu phim mini, b\u1ec3 b\u01a1i, s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 hai h\u1ed3 c\u00e2u \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 Rooney - Coleen \u0111ang \u1edf M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ca gia dinh song o ca Anh va My thoi gian toi. Anh: NS.\" title=\"C\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh s\u1ed1ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 Anh v\u00e0 M\u1ef9 th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u1ea2nh: NS.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/cc2-8050-1532829488.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh s\u1ed1ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 Anh v\u00e0 M\u1ef9 th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4838","checkdouble":"192330"},{"date":"15:56 30/07","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eb7p song sinh \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00f2ng","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/tien-dao-morata-don-cap-song-sinh-dau-long.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4837","checkdouble":"192332"},{"date":"16:02 30/07","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dybala c\u1eb7p ch\u00e1u g\u00e1i hoa h\u1eadu tennis m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/tien-dao-dybala-cap-chau-gai-hoa-hau-tennis-moi-thoi-dai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta m\u1ea3i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n Juventus s\u1ebd ra sao khi c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Paulo Dybala ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea3i m\u00ea du h\u00ed v\u00e0 y\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng. Dybala \u0111ang say \u0111\u1eafm trong v\u00f2ng tay b\u00f3ng h\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 ch\u00e1u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u tay v\u1ee3t n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng xinh \u0111\u1eb9p Gabriela Sabatini.</h2><h2>C\u1eb7p \u201cg\u00e1i nh\u00e0 t\u00f4ng\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Dybala ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Juventus do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 b\u00f9 h\u1eadu World Cup. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n. Dybala \u0111ang b\u1eadn th\u00e1p t\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i du h\u00ed tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3o Mykonos c\u1ee7a Hy L\u1ea1p. B\u00f3ng h\u1ed3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Dybala l\u00e0 ca s\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi anh, Oriana Sabatini.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/dybala.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ecd Sabatini c\u1ee7a Oriana, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u1ec3 thao th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1ea5y quen quen. H\u1ecd ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 Tango, Gabriela Sabatini. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t Argentina n\u00e0y t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u01a1n n\u1eef US Open n\u0103m 1990, gi\u00e0nh HCB t\u1ea1i Olympic 1988 v\u00e0 t\u1eebng leo l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Gabriela Sabatini n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng h\u01a1n nh\u1edd nhan s\u1eafc nghi\u00eang n\u01b0\u1edbc nghi\u00eang th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi c\u00f2n c\u1ea7m v\u1ee3t thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Gabriela Sabatini \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00e1n cho bi\u1ec7t danh hoa h\u1eadu qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t. Sau n\u00e0y xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 hoa h\u1eadu qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t n\u1eefa nh\u01b0 Maria Sharapova hay Ana Ivanovic. D\u00f9 v\u1eady th\u00ec trong m\u1eaft nhi\u1ec1u fan tennis, Gabriela Sabatini v\u1eabn l\u00e0 hoa h\u1eadu qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t xinh \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOriana l\u00e0 ch\u00e1u g\u1ecdi Gabriela Sabatini b\u1eb1ng c\u00f4 ru\u1ed9t. Oriana kh\u00f4ng th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i c\u1ea7m v\u1ee3t c\u1ee7a Gabriela Sabatini. Song b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i, Oriana may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gene xinh \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 b\u00e0 c\u00f4 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u00ean ngo\u00e0i t\u00e0i ca h\u00e1t, Oriana c\u00f2n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong gi\u1edbi showbiz Argentina v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 vai tr\u00f2 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDybala v\u00e0 Oriana b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1edd th\u00ec c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng khai chuy\u1ec7n c\u1eb7p k\u00e8 v\u1edbi nhau. Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u00ecnh t\u1ee9 gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i trai t\u00e0i g\u00e1i s\u1eafc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean c\u00e1c t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Instagram c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c fan Juve nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Dybala v\u00e0 Oriana l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u00f4i \u1edf h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0.</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00f9ng vui duy\u00ean m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 th\u1ee7a ban \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f2n b\u00ed m\u1eadt gi\u1eefa Dybala v\u00e0 Oriana di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 \u00eam \u1ea3. M\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u0169ng nh\u1edd Gabriela Sabatini m\u00e0 n\u00ean. Gabriela Sabatini \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0. Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u Dybala, Oriana l\u1ea5y c\u1edb sang Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 th\u0103m b\u00e0 c\u00f4 Gabriela Sabatini r\u1ed3i t\u1ea1t qua Italia g\u1eb7p Dybala.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dybala c\u1eb7p ch\u00e1u g\u00e1i hoa h\u1eadu tennis h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dybala c\u1eb7p ch\u00e1u g\u00e1i hoa h\u1eadu tennis h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Chuyen-tinh-Tien-dao-Dybala-cap-chau-gai-hoa-hau-tennis-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u1ef1u tay v\u1ee3t xinh \u0111\u1eb9p Gabriela Sabatini ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u00f4 ru\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Oriana</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOriana t\u1eebng t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh y\u00eau l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh y\u00eau \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 ba m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Ba t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t ga-l\u0103ng, l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n v\u00e0 chung th\u1ee7y. \u00d4ng lu\u00f4n y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng. H\u1ecd l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac b\u00ean nhau\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ng\u1ea3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng tay Dybala, Oriana t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian y\u00eau t\u00e0i t\u1eed Julian Serrano. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 v\u1ebb Serrano \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i cho Oriana t\u00ecnh y\u00eau l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0 c\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y cha m\u1eb9 m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu. Oriana chia tay Serrano cho d\u00f9 c\u00f4 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3 hai v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia tay Serrano kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Oriana nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e1t kh\u00fac \u201cV\u00e0 con tim \u0111\u00e3 vui tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d. G\u1eb7p Dybala, c\u00f4 l\u1ea1i y\u00eau nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a y\u00eau l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, Dybala c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u01b0\u1edfi \u1ea5m l\u1ea1i con tim d\u00ednh v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t t\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Dybala c\u0169ng t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh y\u00eau th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i Antonella Cavalieri. Nh\u01b0ng chuy\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft c\u00f3 h\u1eadu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAntonella sau khi \u201cr\u00fat th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf\u201d v\u1edbi Dybala \u0111\u00e3 chua ch\u00e1t cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cS\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Paulo c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1m ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef v\u00e2y quanh anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ebft ch\u1ebft t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Paulo c\u00e0ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng th\u00ec c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4 g\u00e1i b\u00e1m theo anh \u1ea5y. Paulo \u0111\u00e3 n\u0103m l\u1ea7n b\u1ea3y l\u01b0\u1ee3t th\u1ec1 th\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n l\u0103ng nh\u0103ng. Song t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh \u1ea5y n\u1eefa\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd Dybala vui duy\u00ean m\u1edbi. C\u00e1c fan Juve hi v\u1ecdng chuy\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a Dybala th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4836","checkdouble":"192333"},{"date":"15:43 30/07","title":"Arsenal v\u00e0 Barca c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/11/17/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a Monchi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nzonzi l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Steven Nzonzi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sevilla. Trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u00e0 Barca, Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u00e0 Barca, Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/17/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Steven NZonzi l\u1ecdt l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Nzonzi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Les Bleus \u0111\u0103ng quang \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSteven Nzonzi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m. Arsenal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Sevilla nh\u1ea5t. HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-nham-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-arsenal-thay-rabiot-180-192175.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Nzonzi</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Rabiot t\u1eeb PSG. Barca tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf La Liga, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Roma c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Nzonzi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a Monchi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Steven Nzonzi\" title=\"Steven Nzonzi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/6/5/chelsea-va-leicester-tranh-gianh-tien-ve-tru-cua-sevilla.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Steven Nzonzi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia v\u1eeba thu v\u1ec1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Alisson cho Liverpool, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Roma mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u00e0 Barca, Roma ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Sevilla, Roma c\u00f2n nh\u1eafm Leon Bailey c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4835","checkdouble":"192318"},{"date":"13:53 30/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1eedi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-gui-loi-nhan-toi-nguoi-ham-mo-bong-da-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng 30/7, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn nh\u1ee7 t\u1edbi NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00f4ng qua gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, l\u00fac n\u00e0y HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i U23+3.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1eedi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1eedi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/55b5e8203e6a87.img.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n NHM kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn NHM \u0111\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn l\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cHy v\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eebng giao ch\u1ec9 ti\u00eau cho \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ee9a r\u1eb1ng, d\u00f9 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o giao h\u1eefu hay ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD 2018,\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng Cup tr\u00ean SV\u0110 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3/8 t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y 7/8.\u00a0HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng NHM kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n 100% kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu r\u1ed3i g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t . T\u00f4i mong m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e2u m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, d\u00f9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o th\u00ec v\u1eabn h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i, phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 18. HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 t\u1edbi 7/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad-168-192307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad-168-192307.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD</span><br>\r\nM\u1ee9c ph\u00ed b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 cao l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#111000;background:#fbfbfb\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4834","checkdouble":"192309"},{"date":"14:37 30/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho H\u1ed3ng Duy, l\u1ed9 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 H\u1ed3ng Duy, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau ch\u00ed tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u1ed3ng Duy</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 28/7 v\u1eeba qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf HAGL b\u1ecb r\u00e1ch c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i\u00a0v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo cho hay: \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n, trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ebfn s\u1ed1\u00a0x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 ngo\u00e0i \u00fd mu\u1ed1n. Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Duy c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Duy v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f3 thay Duy\u201d.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho H\u1ed3ng Duy, l\u1ed9 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ecdn qu\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho H\u1ed3ng Duy, l\u1ed9 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ecdn qu\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u1ed3ng Duy</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi t\u1edbi 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i ra 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: \u201cKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh gay g\u1eaft m\u1edbi c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd lo\u1ea1i ai ch\u1ecdn ai v\u00ec c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn Ti\u1ebfn Linh hay ch\u1ecdn Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, ch\u1ecdn \u0110\u1ed3 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng hay kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn. D\u00f9 trong \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 khung nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ebfn s\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea7y Park c\u0169ng n\u00f3i chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ai hay b\u1ecf ai. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfp: \"T\u00f4i xin nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh, 3 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1\u00a0ASIAD\u00a0v\u00e0 k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 sau n\u00e0y cho nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00f3\u00a0l\u00e0: 1. \u0110\u1ea1t n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f3; 2. \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh; 3. C\u00f3 t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch, s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 coi m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u00e2m \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng C\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean SV\u0110QG M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3/8 \u0111\u1ebfn 7/8 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a 4 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic g\u1ed3m Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Uzbekistan, Oman v\u00e0 Palestine.\u00a0Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u00f4ng l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho H\u1ed3ng Duy, l\u1ed9 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4833","checkdouble":"192311"},{"date":"15:16 30/07","title":"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/vi-tri-thu-mon-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-lo-dien-cai-ten-se-phai-o-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1eeb chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo, c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u01afu ti\u00ean kinh nghi\u1ec7m<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp ba th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (Thanh H\u00f3a) v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng (S\u00e0i G\u00f2n). Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb HLV Park Hang Seo, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ai s\u1ebd \u1edf nh\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ai s\u1ebd \u1edf nh\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/vi-tri-thu-mon-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-lo-dien-cai-ten-se-phai-o-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y Park nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh \u01b0u ti\u00ean cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m: \"T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n b\u1edfi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u01b0\u1edbi 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf V-League g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u1edf V-League\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng \u1ed5n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i V-League. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. Trong s\u1ed1 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ai s\u1ebd \u1edf nh\u00e0?<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u00eau ch\u00ed, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed kinh nghi\u1ec7m, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 su\u1ea5t ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i V-League, Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n khi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 ba t\u1ea1i CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n khi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady v\u1edbi ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park, tr\u1eeb khi V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng may ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 l\u00fd do ri\u00eang kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp s\u1ee9c cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eeb xa.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho H\u1ed3ng Duy, l\u1ed9 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-gui-loi-nhan-toi-nguoi-ham-mo-bong-da-viet-nam-168-192309.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1eedi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad-168-192307.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-toshiya-miura-noi-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192292.html\">HLV Toshiya Miura tin \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u00f4m h\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-u23-viet-nam-lai-duoc-vinh-danh-tren-bao-nuoc-ngoai-168-192270.html\">\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh tr\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4832","checkdouble":"192319"},{"date":"15:19 30/07","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, HLV Park Hang Seo \u2018c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda\u2019 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/olympic-viet-nam-dinh-trong-tro-lai-hlv-park-hang-seo-cam-cua-bao-chi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng 30/7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng dai d\u1eb3ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</h2><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u1edf bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 30/7, trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t n\u00e0y ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1edbt lo h\u01a1n b\u1edfi \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/20180729-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-tin-vui-tu-dinh-trong-1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau h\u01a1n 1 th\u00e1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp v\u1edbi gi\u00e1o \u00e1n ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 Choi Joo Young. B\u00e1c s\u0129 Choi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho Park Ji Sung v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tu\u1ea5n Anh. \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng b\u1ecb tr\u00e0n d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00f9ng c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n n\u00ean trung v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian 1 th\u00e1ng r\u01b0\u1ee1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ch\u00ednh HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp m\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Choi Ju Young sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cNh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y, h\u00f4m nay \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau th\u1eddi gian tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. B\u00e1c s\u1ef9 Choi Joo Young l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i n\u00ean t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c nhanh h\u01a1n\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay\u00a030/7, HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ghi h\u00ecnh kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng trong kho\u1ea3ng 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Sau \u0111\u00f3, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e1y \u1ea3nh, m\u00e1y ghi h\u00ecnh n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn cho th\u1ea7y Park cho th\u1ea5y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef b\u00ed m\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho H\u1ed3ng Duy, l\u1ed9 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 H\u1ed3ng Duy, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau ch\u00ed tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad-168-192307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad-168-192307.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD</span><br />\r\nM\u1ee9c ph\u00ed b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 cao l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4831","checkdouble":"192323"},{"date":"15:39 30/07","title":"V\u00e9 xem \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng: VFF \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 4.0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/ve-xem-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-giai-tu-hung-vff-ap-dung-cong-nghe-40.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VFF) \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 4.0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap cho v\u00e9 xem \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3, tr\u00e1nh nguy c\u01a1 \"v\u1ee1 s\u00e2n\".</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">VFF \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 cho v\u00e9<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ASIAD 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tham gia gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i) t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3-7/8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ve xem DT Olympic Viet Nam tai giai tu hung duoc ap dung cong nghe nen kho bi lam gia.\" title=\"V\u00e9 xem \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00ean kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/ve-xem-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-giai-tu-hung-vff-ap-dung-cong-nghe-40.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>V\u00e9 xem \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00ean kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu, m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 cho r\u1eb1ng gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i cao v\u1edbi 4 m\u1ec7nh gi\u00e1 150.000, 200.000, 300.000 v\u00e0 400.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 e ng\u1ea1i vi\u1ec7c mua ph\u1ea3i v\u00e9 gi\u1ea3. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, BTC \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t h\u00e0nh m\u1eabu v\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt cao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eabu v\u00e9 g\u1ed3m hai ph\u1ea7n v\u00e9 gi\u1ea5y v\u00e0 v\u00e9 th\u1ebb. Ph\u1ea7n QR Code \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 hai ph\u1ea7n th\u1ebb nh\u1ef1a v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y, v\u1edbi ch\u00edp \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m tra b\u1eb1ng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ecdc th\u1ebb chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1eeba tr\u00e1nh nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t an ninh, v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu, HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0o nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, th\u1ea7y Park c\u0169ng mong ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ba \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan, Oman v\u00e0 Palestine c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 coi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng tung ra h\u1ebft b\u00e0i. Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u nay, th\u1ea7y Park c\u0169ng c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda b\u00e1o ch\u00ed khi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Palestine (3/8), Oman (5/8) v\u00e0 Uzbekistan (7/8) c\u00f9ng v\u00e0o khung gi\u1edd 19h30.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dinh-trong-tro-lai-hlv-park-hang-seo-cam-cua-bao-chi-168-192323.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, HLV Park Hang Seo &lsquo;c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda&rsquo; b\u00e1o ch\u00ed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vi-tri-thu-mon-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-lo-dien-cai-ten-se-phai-o-nha-292-192319.html\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho H\u1ed3ng Duy, l\u1ed9 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-gui-loi-nhan-toi-nguoi-ham-mo-bong-da-viet-nam-168-192309.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1eedi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-ham-mo-co-the-khong-duoc-xem-olympic-viet-nam-thi-dau-o-asiad-168-192307.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-toshiya-miura-noi-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192292.html\">HLV Toshiya Miura tin \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u00f4m h\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4830","checkdouble":"192325"},{"date":"15:00 30/07","title":"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng cho Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/chelsea-san-sang-ban-willian-va-courtois-cho-real-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Willian. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb ph\u00eda K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.</h2><h2>Real nh\u1eafm 2 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian v\u00e0 Courtois n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian v\u00e0 Courtois n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/chelsea-san-sang-ban-willian-va-courtois-cho-real-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Willian v\u00e0 Courtois ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-dat-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-courtois-180-192010.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Thibaut Courtois</span> r\u1ea5t s\u00e1t sao m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u00eda Chelsea g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWillian th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Real l\u00e0 Barcelona. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia l\u1ea1i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 Malcom.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWillian \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng hot sau k\u1ef3 World Cup \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil. V\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Man United. C\u0169ng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Real b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd h\u01a1n t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u00e1n Willian v\u00e0 Courtois</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 hai ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Real Madrid sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 2 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Chelsea kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t khi t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 hai ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Courtois, Chelsea \u0111ang t\u0103m tia Jack Butland. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Stoke \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng dai d\u1eb3ng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Jordan Pickford c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Blues quan t\u00e2m. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Everton \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Butland v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 d\u1ec5 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u d\u00e0nh cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giroud-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-o-chelsea-172-192310.html\">Giroud n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bakayoko-chi-roi-chelsea-neu-172-192308.html\">Bakayoko ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi Chelsea n\u1ebfu....</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4829","checkdouble":"192313"},{"date":"16:07 30/07","title":"Neymar c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/neymar-co-vai-loi-muon-nhan-gui-fan-ham-mo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t clip qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Neymar \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNeymar th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u00e1i qu\u00e1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ghi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n v\u1ea1, di\u1ec5n tr\u00f2 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch. V\u00e0 khi ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng n\u00e0y b\u1ecb nh\u00e2n r\u1ed9ng, Neymar tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i ph\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf \u0111i sau tr\u1eadn thua \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" title=\"Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/neymar-co-vai-loi-muon-nhan-gui-fan-ham-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u00f4i t\u1ecf ra b\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1ef1, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 k\u1ebb h\u01b0 h\u1ecfng. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f4i khi khi\u1ebfn th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi say m\u00ea, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f4i khi khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. V\u00e0 khi b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y t\u00f4i ng\u00e3, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fac t\u00f4i s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 n\u1ed7i \u0111au n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong g\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. T\u00f4i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1eedi r\u1ee7a, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u, ho\u1eb7c n\u00e9m \u0111i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee9ng l\u00ean m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng khi m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i&rdquo; &ndash; Neymar \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va-197-191719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/12/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va-197-191719.html\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u0169 kh\u00f4ng n\u00e3o m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Neymar</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil t\u1ea1o ra t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t leo thang, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dani Alves l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/neymar-se-som-tro-lai-sau-tham-hoa-tai-world-cup-2018-197-192273.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/neymar-se-som-tro-lai-sau-tham-hoa-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/neymar-se-som-tro-lai-sau-tham-hoa-tai-world-cup-2018-197-192273.html\">Neymar s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng PSG &ndash; HLV Tuchel chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Neymar v\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4828","checkdouble":"192322"},{"date":"15:38 30/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP PSG vs Atletico Madrid 18h35 ng\u00e0y 30/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/psg-vs-atletico-madrid-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp PSG vs Atletico Madrid: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u PSG vs Atletico gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Internationl Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 18h35 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 30/7.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>TH\u00d4NG TIN</h2>\r\nPSG: H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 World Cup nh\u01b0 Neymar, Mbappe hay Di Maria ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp trung.<br>\r\nAtletico: V\u1eafng Costa, Saul, Koke, Godin, Giminez v\u00e0 Filipe.<br>\r\nTheo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, PSG thua c\u1ea3 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Atletico th\u1eafng 6 v\u00e0 thua 2 \u1edf 8 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a PSG v\u00e0 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Atletico \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn PSG thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o ngo\u00e0i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Buffon. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Atletico \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Lemar, Rodri hay Gelson.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp PSG vs Atletico Madrid tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp PSG vs Atletico Madrid tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/nhan-dinh-psg-vs-atletico-madrid-18h35-ngay-307-icc-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PSG vs Atletico Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>PH\u00c1T BI\u1ec2U</h2>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel (PSG): \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u1ed5n h\u01a1n khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\".<br>\r\nHLV Diego Simeone (Atletico): \"Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 PSG tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f2n \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c\",<br>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean. 3/4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Atletico c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng n\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Atletico 1-1 (pen 3-1) Arsenal (ICC 2018) </strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/26/Atletico-1-1-Arsenal.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4827","checkdouble":"192326"}]}